data.description: Explore the charm of this lovely single-story home, situated on almost a quarter-acre, just minutes from Lackland, Sea World, and Alamo Ranch. Conveniently located near 410 and 90, this house features four bedrooms and three bathrooms on a corner lot. Enjoy the nearby neighborhood parks and an elementary school, all within easy walking distance.
